{"tid":590010,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有時真係唔怪得人屌鳩你的士狗","createTime":"2018-03-12T09:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T09:43:01.000Z","uid":5928,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"51da80d2c3a5c742886449e182277476928f3ac0","tid":590010,"uid":5928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"話說今朝飛返香港係機場飛的出市區<br />\n咁成身帶得一個hard carry size嘅背囊<br />\n上車都冇野 落車佢無啦啦話要我加6蚊行李費<br />\n我話呢個背囊仔放我個位腳底咋喎點解要收錢<br />\n佢同我講個個都將個行李箱放喺架車入面咪下下唔使收錢<br />\n我話我坐飛機都唔使額外收錢嘅hand carry你同我攞行李箱比 背囊咋喎<br />\n屌你佢夠膽死同我講超過兩呎就要比喎<br />\n我即刻屌佢60cm都未夠點撚樣兩呎<br />\n最尾死都唔撚比 結果死死氣話唔收啦唔收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddf57d6cb5060f7792517157a62560f84f45f87","tid":590010,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"咁你個袋有幾大?"},{"pid":"38c2e1d61f64c037f163dd454656fda40bc45b48","tid":590010,"uid":28831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"擺得入車就唔撚洗加架啦<br />\n上次我拎埋gip上車都唔洗加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c40356e9f2267fb6de4507a3a37d8085dbdd27","tid":590010,"uid":5928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ddf57d6cb5060f7792517157a62560f84f45f87","tid":590010,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"咁你個袋有幾大?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"細過hand carry size limit小小 轉頭cap上嚟<br />\nbtw一定上得的士 有乜可能飛機都hand carry得 的士唔得 佢真係好撚有趣"},{"pid":"5a8bc3190e4b2d6c88af78c87ace97680c746eb8","tid":590010,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"38c2e1d61f64c037f163dd454656fda40bc45b48","tid":590010,"uid":28831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"擺得入車就唔撚洗加架啦<br />\n上次我拎埋gip上車都唔洗加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"咪戇鳩, 超過尺寸一樣要俾<br />\n<br />\n1. 行李附加費：<br />\n<br />\n一般來說，司機可就下列行李，收取行李附加費：<br />\n<br />\n每件擺放在車尾行李廂內的行李；或<br />\n每件<span style=\"color: red;\">擺放在車廂內</span>而長、闊、高總和超過140厘米的行李。"},{"pid":"0ab922a62f1d4cfb56d2037aa4aa9020e95f4b9b","tid":590010,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"比隻的士狗個名黎"},{"pid":"ec27d37da9d35791594385f0a06cffdd4408eac8","tid":590010,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"合理喎，除非你拎緊soft carry"},{"pid":"07bc682f13e3437c9743403ed0cd5b1385d2319a","tid":590010,"uid":5928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"我帶大箱就話要收姐 個袋上得機有咩可能唔上得的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/171437_2b8010ed9ee59c2dd9fb62447ecb475d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F171437_2b8010ed9ee59c2dd9fb62447ecb475d.png&h=75b711e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/171443_2bcd1bd865d9654d0111b9d319b9e81f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F171443_2bcd1bd865d9654d0111b9d319b9e81f.png&h=a8b23c95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a181dc6111ba97b7370f681432f8898ef3bf7ce1","tid":590010,"uid":5928,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ec27d37da9d35791594385f0a06cffdd4408eac8","tid":590010,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"合理喎，除非你拎緊soft carry"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/171646_